One question, why does the update need access to my phone number, see when a call is active, etc?
replyContent:
It doesn't access your phone number, but asks the phone for your geographical region so it can set the default climate zone. Unfortunately the permission to do this is bundled in with the rest of the phone permissions.

And now I've found that the permission isn't needed after all, so the app doesn't ask for it anymore!
